## API Endpoint Mapping

All components are wired to existing backend endpoints:

### Academic Management
- `GET /api/admin/academic/sessions` - List sessions
- `POST /api/admin/academic/sessions` - Create session
- `GET /api/admin/academic/programs` - List programs
- `GET /api/admin/academic/programs/:id?semester=X` - Get subjects by semester
- `GET /api/admin/academic/assignments` - List assignments
- `PUT /api/admin/academic/assignments/:id` - Update assignment

### Examination
- `GET /api/admin/exams` - List exams
- `POST /api/admin/exams` - Create exam
- `GET /api/teacher/marks?exam_id=X&subject_id=Y` - Get students for marks entry
- `POST /api/teacher/marks` - Save marks
- `GET /api/admin/results?exam_id=X&program=Y&semester=Z` - Get results
- `POST /api/admin/results/process` - Process results (calculate SGPA)
- `GET /api/admin/transcript/:studentId` - Generate transcript
- `GET /api/student/report-card` - Get student report card

